{
  "texts": [
    "The method's drawbacks include the lack of standardization [4,83].",
    "• Music This method is implemented by playing music for participants.",
    "The advantages are that it is easy and simple, highly standardized, and emotions develop with time-lapse (15-20 min.).",
    "The drawbacks are that the music taste might influence the experienced emotions.",
    "Additionally, this method gives only the moods either positive or negative."
  ]
}